Date: Wed, 25 Jun 2025 00:13:26 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 03/10] UPSTREAM: DP: wifi: ath12k: Add Rx TLV Filter
 Configuration API's for monitor mode

With the Unified Driver framework, Rx monitor supports two different
architectural models quad ring(mon1) and dual ring(mon2), each models
uses different rings for TLV filter configurations.

To support this, the Filter framework introduces the following APIs
to configure TLV filters for monitor mode in both models:
setup:Configures TLV filters and stores them in the 2D filter array for
      monitor mode.
reset:Clears TLV filters from the 2D filter array for monitor mode.
update:Updates the configured TLV filters to FW using the ring selection
       configuration command.

Patch-dependency:
	0405-0002-UPSTREAM-DP-wifi-ath12k-Add-Rx-TLV-Filter-Configurat.patch

Signed-off-by: Sushant Butta <sbutta@qti.qualcomm.com>
